12.	Using a while loop write a Java program to compute the sum of odd numbers from 1 to 50. 
(3 marks) 
public class Sum {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int sum = 0;
        int number = 1;

        while (number <= 50) {
            if (number % 2 != 0) { 
                sum += number;
            }
            number++;
        }

        System.out.println("The sum of odd numbers from 1 to 50 is: " + sum);
    }
}
